  findDiagonal-aux w k acc (suc fuel) wРѕИaccРЅцsf k<Tsw TwРЅцk accРЅцw with w РЅЪ acc
  ... | yes wРЅАacc = findDiagonal-found fuel k acc (subst (╬╗ x Рєњ k <рхЄ triangular (suc x) РЅА true) (sym wРЅАacc) k<Tsw)
  ... | no wРЅбacc =
