    (w РѕИ (k РѕИ triangular w) , k РѕИ triangular w)             РЅАРЪе cong (╬╗ x Рєњ (w РѕИ x , x)) (cantorPair-triangular-diff m n) РЪЕ
    (w РѕИ n , n)                                              РЅАРЪе cong (╬╗ x Рєњ (x , n)) (m+nРѕИnРЅАm m n) РЪЕ
    (m , n) Рѕј

  -- For cantorPair-unpair, we need the reverse direction
  -- If cantorUnpair k = (m, n), then cantorPair m n = k

  -- Helper: a + (b - a) = b when a РЅц b
