    findDiagonal-TwРЅцk-aux fuel k acc TaccРЅцk with k <рхЄ triangular (suc acc) | inspect (k <рхЄ_) (triangular (suc acc))
    ... | true | _ = TaccРЅцk  -- We stop and return acc
